cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR, cs.MM

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with visual recognition tasks and proposes a method to improve few-shot learning on a fine-grained dataset.
2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper proposes a self-paced learning approach to select high-quality images for training a classifier.
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper proposes a novel approach to address the shortcoming of state-of-the-art approaches in scarce data regimes.
4. cs.GR (Graphics) is a possible category as the paper proposes using a 3D model derived from training images to hallucinate novel viewpoints and poses for scarce samples.
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) is also a possible category as the paper deals with visual recognition tasks and proposes a method to improve few-shot learning on a fine-grained dataset.
